<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/711745-i-know-that-this-is-book-one-point-five-in">I know that this is book one-point-five in THE ILYON CHRONICLES, but it is also the prequel novella. So should I read this or RESISTANCE first?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_711745'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F25740919-half-blood">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/711745-i-know-that-this-is-book-one-point-five-in">5 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/711745-i-know-that-this-is-book-one-point-five-in">Add your answer</a>
</li>
